"### Birth weight in grams
This calculates the birth weight in metric units.
```
var promises = use(["birth_weight_lbs", "birth_weight_oz"]);
```

Here is the calculation, converting the ounces into pounds, summing them up and converting them to grams:
```
Promise.all(promises).then( function() {
  var data = new DataFrame(allMeasures);
  data = data.map(row => row.set('birth_weight', 1000*(row.get('birth_weight_lbs')+(row.get('birth_weight_oz')/16))/2.2));
  update(data, 'birth_weight');
});
```
